      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jonathan Rosenthal</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"https://www.tagesanzeiger.ch/kultur/diverses/der-showdown-kann-beginnen/story/21199877\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1/16/JonathanRosenthal.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"301\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:JonathanRosenthal.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jonathan Rosenthal <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Jonathan Rosenthal</b>,<br />\na Swiss chess <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FIDE_titles#FIDE_Master_(FM)\">FIDE Master</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, former U14 master of Switzerland, and computer scientist affiliated with <a href=\"/ETH_Zurich\" title=\"ETH Zurich\">ETH Zurich</a>. He made first chess programming experience in writing a chess engine dubbed <i>The Machine</i>, which played at <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">HGM's</a> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Online_Engine_Blitz_Tourneys&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Online Engine Blitz Tourneys (page does not exist)\">Online Engine Blitz Tourney</a> in January 2015 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. In the meantime, he graduated at ETH with his <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Science\">Bachelor of Science</a> thesis on <a href=\"/Deep_Learning\" title=\"Deep Learning\">deep lerning</a> in <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, which covers aspects of computer chess versus computer Go, along with <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">search</a> and <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">evaluation</a> topics such as <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">alpha-beta</a>, <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a>, and <a href=\"/Neural_Networks#Deep\" title=\"Neural Networks\">deep neural networks</a> as used in <a href=\"/Matthew_Lai\" title=\"Matthew Lai\">Matthew Lai's</a> thesis chess engine <a href=\"/Giraffe\" title=\"Giraffe\">Giraffe</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php?title=DeepMind&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"DeepMind (page does not exist)\">DeepMind's</a> <a href=\"/index.php?title=AlphaGo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"AlphaGo (page does not exist)\">AlphaGo</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Winter</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2016_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Chess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Programming\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Programming</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Winter\">Winter</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Winter\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Jonathan Rosenthal's second chess programming approach started in 2016 as a group project in a university course on parallel computing along with Jonas Kuratli and Jonathan Maurer. Influenced by his <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a> experience in the domain of Go, after removing the parallel portion of the code, the project evolved to an <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> called <a href=\"/Winter\" title=\"Winter\">Winter</a>, released on January 08, 2018 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.research-collection.ethz.ch/handle/20.500.11850/156354\">Deep Learning for Go</a></i>. B.Sc. thesis,  <a href=\"/ETH_Zurich\" title=\"ETH Zurich\">ETH Zurich</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015\">2015</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55113&amp;start=6\">Re: Weak engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 28, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55355\">Value of a Feature or Heuristic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55375\">I think my engines tuning might be off...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 17, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55453\">Knight Evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 24, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55566\">Questions in Respect to Code Release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 05, 2015</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016_...\">2016 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2016 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=60730\">Long Time No Read</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 07, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63181\">Bayesian Evaluation Functions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63326\">Ridiculous QSearch Depth</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Depth\" title=\"Depth\">Depth</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66266\">Winter Released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jonathan Rosenthal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess\">Chess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Chess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=1315684\">Rosenthal, Jonathan FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/perl/chessplayer?pid=118860\">The chess games of Jonathan Rosenthal</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.svwinterthur.ch/schachwoche08/indexEngl.html\">Winterthur Chess Week 2008 -- Home page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sgzurich.ch/pages/turniere/teamcup.php\">SG Zürich - Teamcup</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Martin_Fierz\" title=\"Martin Fierz\">Martin Fierz</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Programming\">Programming</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Programming\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/rosenthj\">rosenthj · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/rosenthj/Winter\">GitHub - rosenthj/Winter: UCI Chess Engine</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jonathan_Rosenthal&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsect